examples.en: Colombia is watered by several rivers.
Have the horses been fed and watered?
The ale must have been watered down.
The garden is crying out to be watered.
examples.ru: Деревья в этом саду крайне нуждаются в поливе.

examples.en: He roared with laughter until his eyes watered.
My mouth watered at the prospect of a good dinner.
examples.ru: У меня потекли слюнки в предвкушении хорошего обеда.

examples.en: They fed and watered the horses in the barn.
examples.ru: В конюшне они накормили и напоили лошадей.
